        <div class="items">
            <ul>
                <li>Focus on keywords instead of reading every word.</li>
                <li>Avoid subvocalization (saying words in your head).</li>
                <li>Use a pointer or guide to keep your eyes moving.</li>
                <li>Practice reading groups of words at once.</li>
                <li>Start with easier material and increase difficulty gradually.</li>
